Neither these presentations nor the accompanying oral presentations shall constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to buy securities, nor shall there be any sale of securities in any state or jurisdiction in which such offer, solicitation or sale would be unlawful prior to registration or qualification under the securities laws of any such state or jurisdiction. No part of these communications shall form the basis of, or be relied on in connection with, any contract or investment decision under any circumstance for any purpose.

